title: Aerosmith - Rock This Way,Winterhurer Musikfest(2-CD)1990ak320
description:
Aerosmith - Rock This Way,Winterhurer Musikfest(2-CD)1990ak320

Recorded Live at Winterthurer Musikfest,Winterthur,Switzerland - August 31, 1990.
Excellent Soundboard Recording - CBR 320ak
 Superb FM Broadcast in excellent stereo. Concert carries a good selection from Permanent Vacation and Pump. Surprising to see the band open with Train (as per Mama Kins 1994) and the inclusion of One Way Street as the first of five encores. On the insert, Heart's Done Time is listed as My Girl and One Way Street as My Baby.
